/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時已經長期飲暖水<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89cf58d6be6351d0997b39ef9d9d38a190df44c","tid":119693,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T16:22:27.000Z","msg":"冰人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f390eaa22e99713f070eb5ab796888474effcd6","tid":119693,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T16:47:39.000Z","msg":"9月出世 冬天隻腳冰一樣咁凍 成日唔小心隻腳板掂到身體其他地方即刻醒晒"},{"pid":"b79911c24da7e92dcb7e508f22f2afb962a2e162","tid":119693,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T17:24:20.000Z","msg":"手腳凍影響到生活? 影響到自己咩? 影響到掂你嘅人姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個身唔覺凍咪得"},{"pid":"881d827680b7230af422a84694b2f28259a2f2fb","tid":119693,"uid":14361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T17:29:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利申：有跑開步</blockquote><br />\n等我仲跑密左,原來無用架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4031fd9c92d9403342360ccccfa6aecf326b4721","tid":119693,"uid":14361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T17:30:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十二至五月為寒底，六至十一月為熱底，絕對關事，呢d係天生血氣虛，如果唔係坊間咁多古老保品要黎做乜？，寒底主針對女性，男性都會有，但不會有太大影響</blockquote><br />\n我7月出生都係咁"},{"pid":"c504239da79d7157f5a5ac50f7aeae1591d07efa","tid":119693,"uid":25598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T17:33:22.000Z","msg":"我日日打J 隻手四季都咁熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccaae874c8e30d3a12e0cf3e6b563be408093c95","tid":119693,"uid":14524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T17:35:06.000Z","msg":"一月出世<br />\n唔覺凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a78586ab02d85f3a188d83f753f37bfc0848ade","tid":119693,"uid":76008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"